		<body>
				<p rend="align(center)"><placeName>No. 98 Bowery</placeName></p>
				<p rend="align(center)indent(1)"><placeName>New York</placeName> <date>May 6&#47;67</date></p>
				<p>To the Editor of the Occident</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)"><placeName>Philadelphia Penn</placeName></p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">Enclosed I send<lb/> you an advertisement of mine cut<lb/> out of the Jewish Leader of this City<lb/> desiring to ascertain what will<lb/> be the charge to have it inserted<lb/> in the Occident for the term of<lb/> three months and how often the<lb/> Occident is issued during that<lb/> term. to which I will be thankful<lb/> for an immediate reply. I<lb/> also sent this day a few copies<lb/> of the Explanatory pamphlet which<lb/> explains more fully the nature<lb/> and details of the series of pic<lb/>tures also a few newspaper comments<lb/> to which will be added next<lb/> week that of <persName>Rev. Dr. Isaac&#39;s</persName></p>
			<pb n="2"/>
				<p>who pronounces them Gem.<add>&#63;</add> S.<lb/> I have rectified an error committed<lb/> in the printing of said advertisement<lb/> which should read  From<lb/> 7.50 to &#36;30.00 a sett and<lb/> not &#36;3.00</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Awaiting your reply</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">I remain Yours Respy</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><persName role="author">M. Samelson</persName></p>
		</body>
	</text>
